===Etymology===
From Latin '''[[Georgius]]''', from Greek '''[[Γεώργιος]]''' ('''[[georgios]]'''), ''[[farmer]]''

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔː(r)dʒ|-ɔː(r)dʒ]]

===Proper noun===
'''George'''
# A male or female [[given name]].

